author: Tatiana Bautzer and Joel Schectman
description: The brothers whose deft dealmaking helped build JBS SA into the world's No. 1 meat processor are testing that talent like never before as they seek a leniency deal with prosecutors after admitting to paying millions of dollars in bribes to Brazilian politicians.
title: JBS brothers test dealmaking skills in Brazil plea deal showdown
